1502
01:52:16,792 --> 01:52:18,000
I hate her.

1503
01:52:18,917 --> 01:52:20,875
And if you want to
continue talking about her...

1504
01:52:21,333 --> 01:52:22,708
then this interview is over!

1505
01:52:22,792 --> 01:52:23,917
I didn't know that...

1506
01:52:24,000 --> 01:52:26,417
