1519
01:53:35,000 --> 01:53:36,375
Do you have five rupees?

1520
01:53:38,167 --> 01:53:39,417
Five rupees?

1521
01:53:41,000 --> 01:53:43,458
When I first tried to get
into films, someone told me...

1522
01:53:43,583 --> 01:53:45,708
