thanks to our enmity.

1530
01:54:16,708 --> 01:54:18,250
Why did I go to her?

1531
01:54:18,333 --> 01:54:19,625
For company?

1532
01:54:20,208 --> 01:54:22,875
For lack of a friend,
an enemy would do.

1533
01:54:34,708 --> 01:54:36,167
