yourself some respect in your words.

1536
01:54:45,250 --> 01:54:47,125
Anyway, what are you doing here?

1537
01:54:47,708 --> 01:54:49,750
For lack of a friend,
an enemy will do.

1538
01:54:52,708 --> 01:54:54,500
I've destroyed you...

1539
01:54:55,750 --> 01:55:00,083
I was here to see how
many stitches Silk needs.

1540
01:55:03,333 --> 01:55:05,125
Have a coffee... I'll pay for it.

1541
01:55:07,708 --> 01:55:09,375
Two Silk coffees, please.

1542
01:55:13,500 --> 01:55:15,708
The coffee that goes by
my name is quite famous.

1543
01:55:16,417 --> 01:55:17,542
Try it.

1544
01:55:17,625 --> 01:55:19,375
It's the best cure for a hangover.

1545
01:55:21,500 --> 01:55:22,875
You will burn in hell!

1546
01:55:23,042 --> 01:55:24,250
