were caught in a duel.

1549
01:55:52,917 --> 01:55:56,375
I guess I was too high
that I began to like Silk.

1550
01:55:56,792 --> 01:55:58,000
The mind warned...

1551
01:55:58,083 --> 01:56:00,333
‘Don't be an idiot, control yourself.'

1552
01:56:00,667 --> 01:56:03,000
