1564
01:56:52,625 --> 01:56:55,667
That I offer you a
drink and let you abuse me?

1565
01:56:58,458 --> 01:57:00,500
I want a drink because
I don't want to abuse.

1566
01:57:01,958 --> 01:57:03,542
I think you're the type of girl...

1567
01:57:03,625 --> 01:57:05,625
