1576
01:57:42,125 --> 01:57:43,958
Even children wear
more clothes than you.

1577
01:57:58,917 --> 01:58:02,042
If you manage to live
up to a ripe old age...

1578
01:58:02,542 --> 01:58:04,708
you will look
exactly like your mother.

1579
01:58:06,000 --> 01:58:07,333
That's not my mother...

1580
01:58:07,417 --> 01:58:08,708
it's me!

1581
01:58:10,042 --> 01:58:12,500
Nayla wanted to interview my mother.

1582
01:58:12,792 --> 01:58:14,792
You know Nayla...

1583
01:58:14,917 --> 01:58:17,083
she can be very persistent.

1584
01:58:18,125 --> 01:58:20,000
It was not easy to say 'no' to her...

1585
01:58:20,083 --> 01:58:21,917
but it was easy to
become my own mother.

1586
01:58:22,458 --> 01:58:25,292
So... I dusted my hair with powder,
wore a dull saree...

1587
01:58:25,375 --> 01:58:27,042
and gave the interview.

1588
01:58:28,792 --> 01:58:30,625
