embarrassed they gave birth to me.

1593
01:58:48,792 --> 01:58:51,208
If you weren't born at all,
how would the world ever know...

1594
01:58:51,292 --> 01:58:53,333
that women can also be like you!

1595
01:58:56,333 --> 01:58:57,583
Is that an abuse
disguised as praise...

1596
01:58:57,667 --> 01:58:59,667
or praise concealed in an abuse?

1597
01:59:03,000 --> 01:59:05,125
I can't praise you...

1598
01:59:06,042 --> 01:59:08,500
